<div class="home_image_background"></div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="section_wrapper">
    <p class="center-align">
      2020 has been a crazy year.
    </p>
    <p class="center-align">
      We got engaged 10/29/2019 and were so excited to plan our wedding.
      We had no idea we'd be planning it during a pandemic!
    </p>
    <p class="center-align">
      Due to the circumstances with COVID-19, we've had to cancel our previous plans and are doing a micro-wedding at the
      end of August 2020. Unfortunately, capacity is extremely limited due to state regulations and rules provided by the
      venue. <span class="bold">Only immediate family members and the wedding party are allowed to physically attend.</span>
      We hope you understand our difficulty in this decision.
    </p>
    <p class="center-align">
      We still want you to celebrate with us!
    </p>
